{
  "text": "Personal and social responsibility. The personal and social responsibility questionnaire (PSRQ; [CITATION_1] ) is a 14-item questionnaire to quantitatively assess novice instructors' perceived personal and social responsibility. Ratings are based on a 6-point Likert scale (1 = strongly disagree and 6 = strongly agree).",
  "correct_citation": {
